QCT_Simple_Customer_order_Enhancements_W: Test Case 1:If a QCT trade price occurs better than the TOB;QCT order is traded
Test Case 2:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Bid side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 3:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Ask side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 4:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO on Ask side and MO on Bid side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 5:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB only for MO on Ask side and PO is better than the TOB;QCT order is rejected
Test Case 6:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for MO on Ask side and for PO on Bid side;QCT order is rejected
Test Case 7:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB only for PO on Bid side and MO is better than the TOB;QCT order is rejected
Test Case 8:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for MO on Bid side and PO is better than TOB;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 9:If a QCT trade price occurs worse than TOB for PO and MO on Ask side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 10:If a QCT trade price occurs worse than TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is equal TOB on same side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 11:If a QCT trade price occurs worse than TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is equal TOB on opposit side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 12:If a QCT trade price occurs worse than TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is worse than TOB on opposit side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 13:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is worse than TOB on opposit side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 14:If a QCT trade price occurs better TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is worse than TOB on opposit side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 15:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO on Bid side and MO is worse than TOB on same side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 16:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Bid side;QCT order is canceled
Test Case 17:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is worse than TOB on same side;QCT order is rejected
Test Case 18:If a QCT trade price occurs better than TOB for PO on Ask side and MO is worse than TOB on same side;QCT order is rejected
Test Case 19:If a QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO on Bid side and MO is worse than TOB on opposite side;QCT order is rejected
Test Case 20:QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Ask side;no resting customer orders on TOB;QCT order is traded
Test Case 21:QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Bid side;no resting customer orders on TOB;QCT order is traded
Test Case 22:QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Ask side;no resting orders on TOB;QCT order is traded
Test Case 23:QCT trade price occurs equal TOB for PO and MO on Bid side;no resting orders on TOB;QCT order is traded
